<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>About AlUla</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin:0;
      padding:0;
      box-sizing:border-box;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    body, html {
      height:100%;
    }

    /* الخلفية */
    .background {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100vh;
      background: url('https://www.vision2030.gov.sa/media/yaypdije/elephant-rock.jpg') center center / cover no-repeat;
    }

    /* Overlay لتعتيم الصورة */
    .background::before {
      content:"";
      position:absolute;
      top:0; left:0;
      width:100%;
      height:100%;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5); /* 0.5 = نصف شفافية */
    }

    /* محتوى الصفحة */
    .content {
      position: absolute;
      top:50%;
      left:50%;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
      color:white;
      text-align:center;
      width: 80%;
      max-width: 800px;
    }

    .content h2 {
      font-size:3rem;
      margin-bottom:20px;
    }

    .content p {
      font-size:1.2rem;
      line-height:1.6;
    }

    nav {
      position: absolute;
      top: 20px;
      right: 40px;
    }

    nav a {
      color:white;
      margin-left: 25px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size:16px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

  </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="background">

  <nav>
    <a href="/">Home</a>
    <a href="/about">About Us</a>
    <a href="/booking">Booking</a>
    <a href="<% if (!username) { %>/login<% } else { %>/logout<% } %>">
      <% if (!username) { %>Login<% } else { %>Logout<% } %>
    </a>
    <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
  </nav>

  <div class="content">
    <h2>About AlUla</h2>
    <p>AlUla is rich in heritage and culture, with historical sites such as Madaen Saleh and Elephant Rock.</p>
    <p>Best visiting months: October – March.</p>
    <p>Accommodation: Hotels and guesthouses in Central AlUla.</p>
  </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
